  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The light reveals and brightens, but it is also able to create illusions, like mirages in the desert that can deceive the unwary and offer the magus an unexpected diversion.<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>KNOWN SPELLS</strong><br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you choose this secret, you learn the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.oIzA2MEHwxhtQneU]{Minor Illusion}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">and @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.Bnn9Nzajixvow9xi]{Light}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">cantrip, and when they obtain a level in the secret you learn the corresponding spells indicated in the following table:<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>Cantrips:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.oIzA2MEHwxhtQneU]{Minor Illusion}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.Bnn9Nzajixvow9xi]{Light}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>1st level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.LWTUqKkUQdMAmOe0]{Color Spray}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.BrBZdCCrJRIVg7YX]{Silent Image}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>2nd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.JbxsYXxSOTZbf9I0]{Spiritual Weapon}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.bV3yun6MIuFj71Er]{Moonbeam}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>3rd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.BP3GCwa66IAw1yTG]{Daylight}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.6g3WLOZ2u0EbaLAd]{Hypnotic Pattern}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>4th level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.gXtzz9t1DTzJeLr4]{Locate Creature}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.sTIkQK7KuQNOyY0C]{Hallucinatory Terrain}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>5th level:</strong> @Compendium[world.spells-historia.dsO5vt30j2q3QUAO]{Dawn}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.mbFw57uyfLkyiw5k]{Seeming}<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>MYSTERIES</strong></span><br /><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.yJ4yJAlZGXyXtF0H]{Founding Mystery: Without Fear}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.ZWgsOHVV0OSI15ry]{Major Mystery: Glare}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.1weIpdXBf1XzpdcR]{Greater Mystery: Full of Light}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.VGarVRYVUEPOJD3N]{Universal Mystery: Blazing Halo}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>METAMAGIC OF THE SECRET</strong><br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you reach 3rd level in this Secret, you became able to modify the spells they can cast, adapting them to your current needs, and learns the following metamagic options.</span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.v7HWKi3xHaSwodoZ]{Metamagic: Heightened Spell}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.xFBGHjhAlAQBl09J]{Metamagic: Quickened Spell}</span></p>",
